          id: "0300000000E00001",
          type: "item",
          item: "tconstruct:pattern",
          count: 8
        }
      ],
      description: ["Welcome to Tinkers' Construct!", "", "These quests will help you to learn the ropes of this mod and be able to create your own customizable weapons and tools. Let's start out with the most important basic tool.", "", "The manual.", "", " Craft the&l 'M&laterials and You'&r m&ranual. Once you have it, the book willgive you information needed to know how to create most of the things of this mod.", "", "Next we need some &l'Patterns&r&l'&r. Craft some of those up and we can move on to the next step."],
      icon: "tconstruct:materials_and_you",
      rewards: [
        {
          id: "0400000000E00000",
          type: "random",
          table_id: 360287970189705216
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      id: "02000000015D0000",
      title: "Our first Pickaxe, Step One",
      x: 6.5,
      y: 4.5,
      tasks: [
        {
          id: "03000000015D0000",
          type: "item",
          item: "tconstruct:pick_head"
        }
      ],
      description: ["Now that we have stencils, we want to get some tools made. One of the most important tools of course is the pickaxe. I mean it &oIS&r called &l'MIN&l&lE&l&l&l&l&rcraft' for a reason, right?", "", "Anyways lets get some &l'Flint'&r and make our first &l'Pickaxe Head'&r. This will be a good start until we're ready to make the smeltery."],
      icon: "tconstruct:pick_head",
      dependencies: ["02000000015F0000"],
      rewards: [
        {
          id: "04000000015D0000",
          type: "random",
          table_id: 360287970189705216
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      id: "02000000015F0000",
      title: "Parts",
      x: 7.5,
      y: 2.83,
      tasks: [
        {
          id: "03000000015F0000",
          type: "item",
          item: "tconstruct:part_builder"
        }
      ],
      description: ["Alright we've got the stencils, now we need the parts. Make a &l'Part Builder'&r by using one log and a &l'Blank Pattern'&r on top in a crafting grid."],
      icon: "tconstruct:part_builder",
      dependencies: ["0200000000E00000"],
      rewards: [
        {
          id: "04000000015F0000",
          type: "random",
          table_id: 360287970189705216
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      id: "0200000001600000",
      title: "Tool Repair",
      x: 9.5,
      y: 2.83,
      tasks: [
        {
          id: "0300000001600000",
          type: "item",
          item: "tconstruct:tinker_station"
        }
      ],
      description: ["Once we have all the parts, we need to be able to put them together. That's where the &l'Tool Station'&r comes into play. Let's make that so we can put our tools together.", "", "The&l 'Tool Station'&r allows us to put together, repair, and modify only the basic tools. If we want things like the &l'Crossbow'&r or &l'Shuriken'&r, for example, ee'll need the &l'Tool Forge'&r but we'll get to that one a bit later."],
      icon: "tconstruct:tinker_station",
      dependencies: ["0200000000E00000", "02000000015F0000"],
      rewards: [
        {
          id: "0400000001600000",
          type: "random",
          table_id: 360287970189705216
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      id: "0200000001610000",
      title: "Got Grout?",
      x: 9.5,
      y: 4.5,
      tasks: [
        {
          id: "0300000001610000",
          type: "item",
          item: "tconstruct:grout",
          count: 64
        }
      ],
      description: ["Before we can move on from crude tools and weapons, we need to make the smeltery to make all of the good stuff.", "", "To start out, lets get some &l'Grout'&r made. A stack should do nicely, but two stacks would be great. To make &l'Grout'&r, you will need &l'Clay'&r, &l'Sand'&r, and &l'Gravel'&r. If you need the recipe, check &lJEI&r or &l'Materials and You'&r for more details."],
      icon: "tconstruct:grout",
      dependencies: ["0200000001600000"],
      rewards: [
        {
          id: "0400000001610000",
          type: "random",
          table_id: 360287970189705216
        }
      ]
    },
