          type: "item",
          item: "tconstruct:tool_binding"
        }
      ],
      description: ["Finally the last part we need is the &l'Sword Blade'&r and &l'Wide Guard'&r. Why you ask? Well unless you're playing on &oPeaceful&r, we'll need to defend ourself from monsters like those pesky Zombies."],
