      description: ["Okay so we have a few pieces now, but next we'll need to be able to cut trees down. Like we mentioned in the previous quest, using your stumps is quite inefficient.", "", "Let's make the &l'Axe Head'&r. This will make chopping those pesky trees down much easier. And faster too."],
