      description: ["Just like the quest name says, &l'The Seared Tank'&r and the &l'Smeltery Controller'&r are the two items that makes it a Smeltery. The Controller we'll use to put in and monitor what we have in the Smeltery while the Tank is what heats the multiblock structure. You'll need the &l'Seared Brick'&r that you made previously to make these as well as glass for the tank"],
